{"parse":{"title":"Raw Spotted Yellowtail","pageid":113596,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||4}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_01\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=4603\n|charges=1\n|ilvl=45\n|name=Raw Spotted Yellowtail\n|level=35\n|effect=Use: Restores 810 health over 27 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\n\nRaw Spotted Yellowtail can be caught in Azshara, Badlands, Feralas, Stranglethorn Vale, Tanaris and The Hinterlands.\n\n==Raw Spotted Yellowtail as an ingredient==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Spotted Yellowtail}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|4603}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_spotted_yellowtail.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]"}}}